## Architecture & Tech Stack

### Frontend

| Technology | Version | Purpose |
|------------|---------|---------|
| React | 19 | UI framework |
| TypeScript | 5.9 | Type safety (strict mode) |
| Vite | 7 | Build tool, HMR |
| Zustand | 5 | State management (1KB) |
| Tailwind CSS | 3 | Styling |
| Vitest | - | Testing |

### Data Storage (Local-First)

| Layer | Technology | Capacity |
|-------|------------|----------|
| Primary | IndexedDB | 50GB+ |
| Backups | .brain files | Unlimited |
| Auto-save | File System Access API | User folder |

### Performance

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Bundle Size | 117KB gzipped |
| Initial Load | < 1s |
| Code Splitting | 9 feature-based chunks |
| Lazy Loading | Widgets, Calendar, Kanban, AI |

### Project Structure

```
system.knowledgebase/
├── src/
│   ├── pages/           # Dashboard, Tasks, Notes, TimeTracking, Settings
│   ├── widgets/         # 44+ dashboard widgets
│   ├── components/      # Reusable UI components
│   ├── stores/          # Zustand state management
│   ├── services/        # Data persistence, backup, AI
│   └── types/           # TypeScript definitions
├── docs/                # Documentation (56 files)
├── tasks/               # Active development tasks
├── .archive/            # Completed tasks, historical docs
└── .claude/             # Automation tools, templates
```

